<node id="Redis">
  <data key="d0">Redis</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Redis is an in-memory database known for its low latency vector search capabilities, ideal for real-time applications.&lt;SEP&gt;Redis supports in-memory vector search operations with low latency, offering fast retrieval for real-time applications.</data>
