  <data key="d1">programming_language</data>
  <data key="d2">Python is a programming language that facilitates direct integration of LightRAG into applications, allowing for programmatic access and custom workflows.&lt;SEP&gt;Python is a programming language used to run the evaluation script for LightRAG.</data>
