<node id="RAG System Quality">
  <data key="d0">RAG System Quality</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">RAG system quality is evaluated based on several key metrics related to the accuracy and relevance of answers generated by the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0a6a2a571099c70c7e20dbd90da662e2</data>
  <data key="d4">lightrag/evaluation/sample_documents/05_evaluation_and_deployment.md</data>
